<v Interviewer>
Mr L. F. Dibley's 'Finian's Rainbow'. And now over to me. [action] close-up of interviewer. Exclusively on the programme today we have the Foreign Secretary, who has just returned from the bitter fighting in the Gulf of Amman. He's going to tell us about canoeing.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:34.000
[action] River bank seen from opposite side. A canoe is on the bank; a man in pinstripes stands beside it. He coughs and gets in.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:40.000
